# models/ holds local-only LLM weights — symlinks or copies of large GGUF files.
# Nothing in this directory should ever be committed except README.md and this file.
#
# See ../docs/VOCABULARY.md → "Where models and assets live on disk" for the
# split between repo-committed assets (small) vs external/local model weights
# (large, never committed). Anything 100MB+ would fail `git push` anyway —
# GitHub rejects files over that limit without Git LFS, and Git LFS for 16GB
# of model weights is not what we want.

# Ignore everything by default...
*

# ...except the README and this .gitignore.
!README.md
!.gitignore
